[gd_resource type="Theme" format=3 uid="uid://bngith66r6i41"]

; The debug theme — used by debug-only screens and overlays so debug UI can diverge from the shipped look
; without touching default.tres. Buttons mirror default.tres (no restyle); the debug-only text variations:
;   DebugLabel     — the encounter "matches" count readout (debug builds only)
;   DebugWatermark — the on-screen version stamp (debug builds only)

